mso-ansi-language:EN;mso-fareast-language:ZH-TW;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">Cromie,
William J. (18 April 2002). [https://web.archive.org/web/20070524212421/http://www.hno.harvard.edu/gazette/2002/04.18/09-tummo.html "Meditation changes temperatures: Mind controls body in extreme experiments"]. ''Harvard
University Gazette'' (President and Fellows of Harvard College via Internet
Archive)</span></span><span class="reference-accessdate"><span lang="EN" style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";mso-ascii-theme-font:
